# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000293> (has specified input)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000293> "8/17/09: specified inputs of one process are not necessarily specified inputs of a larger process that it is part of. This is in contrast to how 'has participant' works.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000412> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000293> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/obi.owl>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000293> "has specified input"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000293> "The inverse property of 'is specified input of'"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001762> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000293> "PERSON: Alan Ruttenberg"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001762> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000293> "PERSON: Bjoern Peters"@en)
