AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000312> "is specified output of"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000312> "A relation between a planned process and a continuant participating in that process. The presence of the continuant at the end of the process is explicitly specified in the objective specification which the process realizes the concretization of."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001762> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000312> "Alan Ruttenberg"@en)
