# Object Property: <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000023> (is causally responsible for)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/has_curation_status> <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000023> "metadata incomplete")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000023> "is causally responsible for"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000023> "x is causally responsible for y iff x is an Agent, y is a Process, and z is a Process, and x is agent_in z, and z is the cause of y"@en)
ObjectPropertyDomain(<https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000023> <https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001017>)
ObjectPropertyRange(<https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000023> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015>)

# Object Property: <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000024> (is normatively accountable for)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/has_curation_status> <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000024> "metadata incomplete")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000024> "this is not importantly different from causal responsibility's definition (draft)"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000024> "is normatively accountable for"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000024> "x is normatively accountable for y iff x is an Agent, y is a Process, and z is a Process, and x is agent_in z, and z is the cause of y"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000024> "manager is responsible for the subordinate's actions"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000024> "parent is a responsible for a child"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000024> "parent is responsible or a child's actions"@en)
ObjectPropertyDomain(<https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000024> <https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001017>)
ObjectPropertyRange(<https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000024> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015>)

