# Class: <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000040> (Owner Entity Role	)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000040> "Either use IAO_0020027 (d-acts) OR mint a new IRI (worst cast scenario). Original def: A role in a human social process that is based on a social act and whose bearer exercises exclusive control over a property, where this control is permitted by one or more deontic roles, which are parts of the owner role."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000040> "Owner Entity Role	"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000040> "A role that inheres in a person and that, when it is realized, is realized in a social act and whose bearer exercises control over a possession, where this control is permitted by one or more deontic roles, which are parts of the owner role."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://github.com/jonathanvajda/cco-d-acts/ont00000040> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000023>)

